Notcoin Pre-Market 
Notcoin Pre-Market vouchers represent the in-game Notcoin currency, which can be exchanged for $NOT after a token generation event. Please note: For better convenience, we may remove some zeros from the Notcoin balances and vouchers when converting to $NOT (no one likes counting 0.00...zeros in the price of a token, isn’t it?). It's a visual change that will not affect the user's wealth value. Supply: 138410000000 Price: 2.731785106382979
